<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Colorful Student Info</title>
    <style>

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ff9a9e, #fad0c4, #fad0c4, #ffdde1);
            color: #333;
        }

        .head {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ff512f, #dd2476);
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            font-size: 40px;
            font-weight: bold;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(221, 36, 118, 0.8);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .logo-frame {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            border: 5px solid white;
            border-radius: 50%;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .logo-frame img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .logo-frame:hover {
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }

        .menu {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #06beb6, #48b1bf);
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: white;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .menu:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #48b1bf, #06beb6);
        }

        .container {
            display: flex;
            padding: 20px;
            justify-content: space-around;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .left {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #f79d00, #64f38c);
            padding: 20px;
            width: 25%;
            min-height: 300px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-around;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .left:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .left button {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ff7eb3, #ff758c);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            cursor: pointer;
            width: 100%;
            font-size: 18px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .left button:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ff758c, #ff7eb3);
        }

        .right {
            width: 65%;
            padding: 20px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .right:hover {
            transform: scale(1.02);
        }

        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            border-radius: 15px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        th,
        td {
            border: 2px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #333;
        }

        th {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #6a11cb, #2575fc);
            color: white;
        }

        td {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
        }

        tr:hover td {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
          
          .footer {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #8e2de2, #4a00e0);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 18px;
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }

            .left,
            .right {
                width: 90%;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

            .head {
                font-size: 30px;
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 10px;
            }

            .logo-frame {
                width: 80px;
                height: 80px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="head">
        <div class="logo-frame">
            <img src="https://scontent-sin2-3.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t39.30808-6/420085079_751856483661560_4334817942904938040_n.jpg?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6ee11a&_nc_ohc=HS8XyDUDOsgQ7kNvgFohjph&_nc_oc=Adi_0R3BqKBb-kfs4o24WaaFsnbQJTLtxGhVKNRwpBd52uvAPdbL87IKVZn3JE78Hr2byMb4lyJHw5IcY5nOTCbK&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent-sin2-3.xx&_nc_gid=A2f9pCF2aQsmTTcfU-E2D1-&oh=00_AYFQOnbO_giqEqzbOZaetfnKYS1n0rBQHgshF_BZu6Gz0w&oe=67D11FA0"
                alt="Logo">
        </div>
        üåüAnti Breach Measures üåü
    </div>

    <div class="menu">MENU</div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="left">
            <p>Navigation</p>
            <button>üè† Home</button>
            <button>‚ÑπÔ∏è About</button>
            <button>üìû Contact</button>
        </div>

        <div class="right">
            <table>
                <tr>
                    <th colspan="3">Student Info</th>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>Name</th>
                    <th>ID</th>
                    <th>Department</th>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>ABM</td>
                    <td>1131</td>
                    <td rowspan="2">CSE</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>H<sub>2</sub>O</td>
                    <td>123</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">üöÄ Footer üöÄ</div>
</body>

</html>
